            <t:abstract>
                <t:p>A miniature illustrating <t:ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3612Miracle">Miracle of Mary: Miracle of the Phoenician evil man called
          Bārok</t:ref> typically 
                    with as a sequence of two episodes/events, showing: first, ʾAnǝsṭāsyos standing praying in a church before the icon of the <t:ref type="authFile" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/AT1031VirginAndChild">Virgin and Child</t:ref>;
                    second, ʾAnǝsṭāsyos lying before <t:persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS6819Mary">St Mary</t:persName>, who together with the Child is extending her hand towards him.</t:p>
